'''''Bermuda Triangle''''' is a vertically [[scrolling shooter]] released in arcades by [[SNK Playmore|SNK]] in 1987.<ref>{{KLOV game|id=7095}}</ref> The player controls a [[fighter aircraft|fighter jet]] and shoots enemies, collects [[power-up]]s, and defeats [[boss (video gaming)|bosses]] to advance levels.

